Lakshman Mandapati is a B.Tech undergrad in CS, aspiring AI Generalist, Co-Founder of Trinova and Brahamatron AI, with expertise in LLMs, NLP, computer vision, and full-stack AI development.
Guthi Vignesh Babu is a B.Tech undergrad in CSE (AI&ML), aspiring AI/ML engineer with web development and multiple internships in Generative AI, LLMs, predictive modeling, and full-stack development.

instruction: Explain how the founders' skills complement each other.
output: The founders bring complementary strengths. Imadabathuni Harsha Venkat leads AI vision, Lakshman Mandapati builds infrastructure and AI systems, and Guthi Vignesh Babu integrates hardware and ML into real-world projects.
